{"tid":1170234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太空垃圾遺禍】天降「中國衞星碎片」幾乎砸中老撾僧人 97年也曾有太空垃圾擊中人","createTime":"2019-05-25T01:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T09:01:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e0cc13db91d69b5b083f4c57a6d470bec5f49a","tid":1170234,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"老撾一名僧人幾乎遭從天而降的太空垃圾砸中，當地居民相信，這塊金屬片是來自中國的人造衞星。<br />\n事發於接近泰國和柬埔寨邊境的老撾占巴塞省（Champasak），一塊估計是人造衞星脫落的金屬片，差點擊中一群身穿橙色長袍的僧侶。僧侶避過一劫後拿着金屬片拍照，當地傳媒指，碎片相信來自中國。<br />\n若然屬實，今次也並非中國太空垃圾首次墜落地球，去年4月太空實驗室「天宮一號」失控墜毀，不過中國官方聲稱大部份組件在進入大氣層時已被燒毀，不影響地表安全。<br />\n被太空垃圾擊中的機率雖然很小，但也不無機會。1997年，就有首宗太空垃圾擊中人的案例，當年美國俄克拉何馬州一名女子在公園散步時，遭一罐如飲品空罐般重的金屬片擊中肩膀，當年金屬片交由塔爾薩大學（University of Tulsa）地球科學系分析，當時認為屬美國太空總署物料，後來進一步分析相信，它來自三角洲2號運載火箭（Delta II rocket）的燃料缸，1996年曾搭載一枚空軍衞星上太空。<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190524/large/1558686107_e1fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190524%2Flarge%2F1558686107_e1fc.png&h=30a582db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190525/59635133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190525%2F59635133&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62C%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=bce2e79d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190525%2F59635133&h=92fc550a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190525/59635133</a>"},{"pid":"5b4d3d066aba7d2c38219b4b4d96e527ecc12f9d","tid":1170234,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"天礙震星<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEr8QfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEr8QfX.png&h=92b14778&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65def5ba3a4cc053fbb7b2c1515c2d8209255806","tid":1170234,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0320181224f6ea1589188412267acdebc0fc25d3","tid":1170234,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"有無數學家計幾多份之幾先中到?"},{"pid":"f887a9f0ef9c914260789a1b82fc7066031e99bc","tid":1170234,"uid":31920,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0320181224f6ea1589188412267acdebc0fc25d3","tid":1170234,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"有無數學家計幾多份之幾先中到?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"2份之1<br />\n一係中一係唔中"},{"pid":"1ac2201be49429e3962ef9a5d46ecc05ec10cb61","tid":1170234,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f887a9f0ef9c914260789a1b82fc7066031e99bc","tid":1170234,"uid":31920,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0320181224f6ea1589188412267acdebc0fc25d3","tid":1170234,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"有無數學家計幾多份之幾先中到?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"2份之1<br />\n一係中一係唔中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:52:37.000Z","msg":"大數學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c369730e57dc9a850045ac55d5ad053d6148ab86","tid":1170234,"uid":89857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1j4N8mE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1j4N8mE.jpg&h=73affa46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5af7bd86c91bbadfa9065d43caf3ef80223f516","tid":1170234,"uid":133086,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"你話上面有中文字 都叫做有啲理由<br />\n乜線索都冇咁樣開名好似過份啲"}]}